
Welcome to CoreMedia Monitoring Project!

This container holds many tools to handle some monitoring special things.

Try the following
  to *add* a Host to the Monitoring:
    curl -X POST http://localhost/api/$hostname  (e.g. curl -X POST http://localhost/api/blueprint-box)
  this will be creates a set of Grafana Dashboards too

  to *adding force* (fist delete, then re adding)
    curl -X POST http://localhost/api/$hostname/force

  to *remove* a Host from Monitoring
    curl -X DELETE http://localhost/api/$hostname

  to *list all* Host in the Monitoring use this
    curl http://localhost/api/

  to *list one* Host
    curl http://localhost/api/$hostname

